Sama da mutane miliyan 20 a tashoshin talabijin shida sun kalli shaidar shaidu a ranar Alhamis a Kotun Koli a shari'ar tsakanin Brett Cowan da Christina Blasey Ford, wacce ta zarge shi da laifin cin zarafin mata da ya faru a shekarun 1980.
Yayin da zanga-zangar siyasa ke ci gaba, masu watsa shirye-shirye sun katse shirye-shiryen su na yau da kullum don samun labari mai ban mamaki a ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya tsara don FBI: ya kasance don gudanar da binciken mako guda na zargin.
Ford ta gaya wa Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattawa cewa ta tabbata da kashi ɗari bisa ɗari cewa wani ɗan giya mai suna Kavanah ya kama ta kuma ya yi ƙoƙari ya cire mata tufafinta a wani biki a makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh ya ce a cikin shaidarsa mai zafi cewa ya tabbata cewa ba haka ba ne.
Wataƙila mutane sama da miliyan 20.4 da Nielsen ta sanar a ranar Juma'a ne suka kalli bidiyon.
Kamfanin ya ƙididdige matsakaicin yawan masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu bayanai nan take ba ga sauran cibiyoyin sadarwa da suka nuna wannan, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma Nielsen yana da matsala wajen tantance mutanen da suke kallon talabijin a ofis.
Don kwatanta, girman masu sauraro kamar wasan karshe ne ko kuma na Oscar.
"Fox News, wanda masana suka goyi bayan nadin Kavan, ya jagoranci dukkan cibiyoyin sadarwa tare da matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a cikin yini", in ji Nielsen.
ABC ta zo ta biyu da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS ta samu miliyan 3.1, NBC ta samu miliyan 2.94, MSNBC ta samu miliyan 2.89, kuma CNN ta samu miliyan 2.52 a cewar Nielsen.
