AMLO a Mexico ya yi alkawarin ba su yi amfani da sojojin da farar hula
Zababben shugaban kasar Mexico Andres Manuel Lopez Abrador ya yi alkawarin ba zai taba amfani da karfin soja ba a kan fararen hula yayin da kasar ke gab da cika shekaru 50 da kaddamar da zanga-zangar kashe dalibai.
A ranar Asabar a dandalin Tlatelolco Plaza Lopez Abrador ya yi alkawarin ba zai taba amfani da sojoji wajen murkushe mutanen Mexico ba.
A ranar 2 ga Oktoba, 1968, sojoji sun harbe zanga-zangar lumana a dandalin, wanda ya kashe mutane kusan 300, a lokacin da ƙungiyoyin dalibai na hagu suka shiga cikin Latin Amurka.
Lopez Abrador ya yi alkawarin tallafawa matasa 'yan Mexico ta hanyar ba da tallafin wata-wata ga dalibai, ta hanyar samar da karin wuraren zama a jami'o'in gwamnati.
"Rashin aikin yi da rashin damar samun ilimi na jan hankalin matasa su shiga cikin kungiyoyin aikata laifuka", in ji shi.
Amurka kamata ninka kudade ga na'ura hankali
"Yayin da kasar Sin ke kara samun karfin gwiwa a fannin ilimin kere kere, Amurka ta kamata ta ninka kudaden da take kashewa a binciken wannan fasaha", in ji mai saka jari kuma mai binciken ilimin kere kere Kai-Fu Lee, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Wannan magana ta fito ne bayan da wasu bangarorin gwamnatin Amurka suka yi magana game da AI, duk da cewa Amurka ba ta da wata dabarar AI.
A shekarar da ta gabata, kasar Sin ta bayyana shirinta na zama kan gaba wajen kirkiro AI nan da shekarar 2030.
"Sau biyu a kasafin kudin bincike na AI zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, ganin cewa sauran kasashen duniya suna baya da Amurka, kuma muna sa ran ci gaba na gaba a AI", in ji Lee.
"Samun tallafi sau biyu zai ninka yiwuwar cewa babbar fasahar kere kere ta gaba za ta kasance a Amurka", in ji Lee a wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa mai suna Superstate Machine Intelligence: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order ya fito a wannan watan da Houghton Mifflin Harcourt ya wallafa, shi ne babban darektan kamfanin Sinovation Ventures wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI a kasar Sin, Face ++.
A shekarun 1980 a Jami'ar Carnegie-Mellon, ya yi aiki a kan tsarin ilimin injiniya wanda ya zarce babban dan wasan Amurka Atell, kuma daga baya ya zama shugaban Microsoft Research kuma shugaban kamfanin Google na kasar Sin.
Lee ya amince da gasar fasaha ta gwamnatin Amurka kamar gasar robotics ta Hukumar Kula da Bincike ta Tsaro, kuma ya tambaya lokacin da za a yi gaba don taimakawa wajen gano wuraren da za a ci gaba.
"Masu bincike a Amurka sukan yi aiki tukuru don samun tallafin gwamnati", in ji Lee.
"Ba kasar Sin ce ke sace shugabannin jami'a ba, kamfanoni ne", in ji Lee.
