LeBron ya fara aiki a ranar Lahadi a San Diego
Wannan shi ne lokacin da magoya bayan kungiyar Lakers ke jiran ganin LeBron James ya fara buga wasan sa na farko a Los Angeles Lakers.
Kocin Lakers, Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na kakar wasa a ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma minti nawa zai yi har yanzu ba a bayyana ba.
"Zai zama fiye da ɗaya, ƙasa da 48", in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Wakilin Lakers Mike Trudell ya rubuta cewa James zai iya buga wasa a cikin iyakacin minti.
Kamar yadda aka saba yi a wannan makon, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na wasanni shida na kakar wasa.
"Ba na bukatar wasannin wasannin kakar wasa a wannan lokaci na aiki don shirya", in ji shi.
Lokacin jawabin Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
A wannan karon a garin Wheeling, West Virginia, Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara kamfen dinsa na farko.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin jawabai biyar da Trump zai gabatar a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau a Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da yake tabbatar da samun kuri'un da za su cika gurbin kotun kolin, Trump na neman karfafa goyon baya a zaben da ke tafe, yayin da 'yan Republican ke fuskantar rasa iko a majalisar dokoki idan aka kada kuri'un a watan Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne za a fara jawabin Trump a yammacin yau a West Virginia kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon sa a yanar gizo?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, da karfe 7 na yamma, ET, ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon jawabin Trump a West Virginia a yanar gizo a ƙasa a kai tsaye a YouTube.
Trump zai iya yin sauraron sauraron karar da aka yi a wannan makon game da takarar da Brett Kavanaugh ya yi a Kotun Koli, wanda ke fama da zargin cin zarafin mata da ake tsammanin za a amince da shi a majalisar dattijai a cikin mako guda yayin binciken FBI.
Amma babban dalilin wannan jawabin shi ne don taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar zaben a watan Nuwamba.
Don haka, kamfen din shugaba Trump ya sanar da cewa wadannan jawabai biyar da zai yi a mako mai zuwa, an yi su ne domin karfafa masu aikin sa kai da magoya baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, Reuters ta ruwaito.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandar majalisar, don haka shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai iya yayin da muke shiga wani yanayi na kamfen", in ji wani kakakin kamfen din Trump ga kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
An shirya bikin ne a gidan wasan Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, taron na yau zai iya jawo hankalin magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya dauki hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne karo na biyu a cikin wata guda da Trump ya ziyarci jihar West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe da kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jihar West Virginia, Patrick Morris, wanda ke kan gaba a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morris cewa shugaban ya zo ya gwada ba shi damar yin zabe", in ji Simon Heather, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, in ji Reuters.
