Amurka ta ba da ƙarin juriya a wasan ƙwallon ƙafa huɗu, ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma ba za su iya yin wani abu ba.
Don ci gaba da cin kofin, Jim Furyk yana bukatar maki takwas daga wasanni 12 da ya buga a ranar Lahadi.
Fleetwood ita ce ta farko da ta fara buga gasar Turai da ta ci maki hudu a jere, ita da Molinari, wanda aka yi wa lakabi da Molliwood bayan wasan karshen mako mai ban mamaki,  sune biyu kawai da suka ci maki hudu a wasanninsu hudu na farko a tarihin gasar Ryder.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed da hudu, sai suka ci gaba da doke Woods da kuma ɗan wasan Amurka, Bryson DeComb da biyar da huɗu.
Woods, wanda ya yi ritaya daga wasa biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna wani lokaci mai haske, amma yanzu ya rasa 19 daga cikin 29 a wasanni hudu da hudu da bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, ya huta a wasanni hudu, ya sake komawa abokin aikinsa Henrik Stenson a wasanni hudu kafin ya doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepke 2 & 1  duka biyu a duniya.
