Mako guda bayan da jaridar kasar Sin ta buga wani shafi hudu a jaridar Amurka ta yau da kullum, tana ta yaba wa cinikin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka don yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump a ranar Laraba ya ambaci takardar China Daily a jaridar Des Moines Register  jaridar da ta fi kowanne a jihar Iowa  bayan da ya zargi China da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
