'Yan Republican sun kori mata masu jefa kuri'a a gaban zaben tsakiyar shekara bayan da aka yi watsi da zaben Kavanaugh, manazarta sun yi gargadin
Yayin da manyan 'yan Republican da dama ke kare dan takarar babban alkalin kotun kasar Brett Kavanaugh a fuskar zargin cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za su fuskanci wani mummunan sakamako, musamman daga mata, a zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa.
An yi ta nuna motsin rai a kan wannan, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun nuna cewa suna shirye su yi zabe.
"Ba za mu iya mayar da waɗannan abubuwan ba", in ji Grant Richards, farfesa a makarantar siyasa ta Maxwell a Jami'ar Syracuse, ga wata kasida da aka buga a ranar Asabar.
