Muna da wasanni 12 da za mu buga gobe, amma muna son fara wasa da sauri kamar yadda muka gani a Brooklyn da Madina.
Idan ka ci gaba da saurin gudu, matsin lamba mafi girma yana kan wadanda suke wasa a tsakiyar wasan.
Mun tsara jadawalin kuma mun sanya 'yan wasan yadda muke so, kuma za mu yi kokarin samun wasu sihiri gobe.
Thomas ya fara wasa kuma yana fuskantar Rory McIlroy a wasan farko, yayin da Paul Casey, Justin Rose, John Romm, Tommy Fleetwood da John Poulter za su yi wasa da manyan 'yan wasan golf.
