Saukowa na sabon Jamus warship sake jinkirta
An shirya sabuwar jirgin ruwan sojin ruwa na Jamus ya shiga aiki a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma ba zai zo ba kafin shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma karuwar farashin, a cewar rahotannin kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
An jinkirta ƙaddamar da Rheinland-Pfalz, babban jirgi na sabon rukunin Baden-Wuerttemberg, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019, kamar yadda jaridar Die Zeit ta rubuta, tana ambaton wani jami'in soja.
An shirya cewa jirgin zai fara aiki a shekarar 2014, amma matsaloli da suka taso bayan gina shi sun hana wannan shiri mai matukar muhimmanci.
Jiragen ruwa hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg, da aka ba da umarni a shekara ta 2007, za su maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Za su kasance da makamai masu ƙarfi, da makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami, da wasu fasahohin fasaha, kamar rage gani ga radar, infrared da siginar sauti.
Daga cikin wasu muhimman halaye  tsawon lokaci tsakanin kulawa  sababbin jiragen ruwa ba za su iya shiga tashar jiragen ruwa ba har zuwa shekaru biyu.
Amma jinkiri na ci gaba da faruwa yana nufin cewa jiragen ruwa na zamani  da zasu iya ba Jamus damar nuna ikonta a kasashen waje  zasu tsufa kafin a fara amfani da su, in ji Die Zeit.
An buga labarin jirgin ruwan F125 a shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da rundunar sojin ruwa ta Jamus ta ƙi karɓar jirgin kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa tashar jirgin ruwa ta Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
A karo na farko, Rundunar Sojan Ruwa ta dawo da jirgin zuwa tashar jiragen ruwa bayan an kawo shi.
Ba a san dalilin dawowar ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun rubuta game da yawancin "kurakurai a cikin software da kayan aiki" wanda ya sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani a cikin aikin yaki.
Rashin kayan aiki na musamman yana da mahimmanci, saboda jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg suna da kawai 120 sailors  rabin ma'aikatan tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An kuma gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyi sosai, wanda ke rage aikinsa kuma yana iyakance damar da za a iya inganta shi.
Rhineland-Pfalz tana da nauyin tan 7,000, wanda ya ninka nauyin jirage iri ɗaya da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Ban da kayan aiki da suka lalace, farashin aikin  har da horar da ma'aikatan  ma ya zama matsala.
Farashin ya kai Euro biliyan 3.1 (dala biliyan 3.6)  daga farkon Euro biliyan 2.2.
Matsalolin da ke tattare da sababbin jiragen ruwa sun zama masu mahimmanci a yayin da ake gargadin cewa sojojin Jamus na raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro a majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya ce rundunar sojin ruwa na Jamus tana da ƙananan jiragen ruwa da za su iya yin aikin soja.
Ya ce matsalar ta kara tsanantawa yayin da jiragen ruwa ke lalacewa kuma babu sauran jirage da za a maye gurbinsu.
Ya yi korafin cewa babu wani daga cikin jiragen ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg da zai iya shiga cikin Navy.
