Ga wasu abubuwa game da Paula da Dongal a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne, wanda ke ƙarshen wani ɗan ƙaramin bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan jama'a 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin da aka yi girgizar ƙasa da tsunami, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafa shi.
Donggala  Regency, wanda ya shimfida a cikin fiye da mil 180 (300 km) na bakin teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gundumar  yanki ne na yanki wanda ke ƙasa da lardin, a cikin 2017 ya ƙidaya mutane 299,200.
Kifi da aikin gona sune tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Har ila yau, hakar nickel yana da mahimmanci ga lardin, amma an mayar da hankali ne a Moraval, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
A cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'o'i ta Indonesia, an yi wa Palau da Donggala tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200, kuma an lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Wani tsunami kuma ya afkawa yankin Donggala na yamma a shekarar 1996, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake samun girgizar kasa a cikin tekun Pacific kuma ana yawan samun girgizar kasa.
Ga jerin manyan girgizar kasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Oche na kasar Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afku a kasashe 14, wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 226,000 a duk gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabinsu a Oche.
2005: A jerin manyan girgizar kasa buga a yammacin Coast na Sumatra a karshen Maris ko farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 6.8 ta afku a kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afku a gabar teku ta kudu, inda ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: A birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma, wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin maki 7.6 ta auku.
Mutane sama da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 ta afku a tsibirin Mintovaia a bakin tekun Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10, ta lalata kauyuka da dama kuma ta kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa mai rauni ta afkawa garin Pidie Jaya a lardin Oche, ta haddasa barna da firgici, kamar yadda ta tunatar da mutane game da lalacewar girgizar kasa da tsunami na shekarar 2004.
Amma ba a yi tsunami ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a ƙarƙashin ginin da ya rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lamboc na Indonesia, ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta hana dubban masu yawon bude ido barin ƙasar.
