Ofishin lauya na tarayya ya bukaci hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da kai harin New York
Ofishin Shari'a na tarayya a New York na neman hukuncin kisa ga Saiful Saifov, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taba yi wa wani laifi ba tun 1953.
Saifov, mai shekara 30, a watan Oktoba ya yi amfani da wata motar haya ta Home Depot don ya hau kan hanyar keke a kan hanyar West Side a Lower Manhattan, yana kashe masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu keke a hanyarsa.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, bisa ga sanarwar niyyar neman hukuncin kisa da aka gabatar a gundumar kudu ta New York, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saif ya yi wa mutane takwas dūka da gangan kuma ya yi wa jiki mummunan rauni.
Bisa ga bayanan kotu, duka laifuffukan biyu suna da hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun bincike ta tarayya ta ba Saipov zargi da zargin da aka yi masa na abubuwa 22, ciki har da zargin da aka yi masa na kisa don tallafawa harin; wannan sashi ne da masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da shi a lokuta na aikata laifuka da kuma zargin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "shirye-shiryen da aka yi da gangan" kuma sun yi amfani da kalmomi kamar "abin ƙyama, mummunan aiki da lalata" don bayyana laifukan da Saifova ya aikata.
Saifula Habibulayevich Saifov ya haifar da rauni, ya lalata da kuma rasa iyalan da abokai na Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Anne-Lori Decadtt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erli, Ernan Ferruccio, Ernan Diego Mendes da Alejandro Damiano Pagnola, an fada a cikin sanarwar niyya.
Mutum biyar da suka mutu 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da aka fara shari'ar kisa a gundumar kudu ta birnin New York.
An yanke wa mai kara Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa kan wasu masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi biyu amma a karshe an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka yi amfani da hukuncin kisa a New York a shari'ar tarayya ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka yanke wa hukuncin kisa bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa shekaru biyu da suka gabata saboda yin rahoto ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War.
An kashe ma'auratan Rosenberg a kan kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan kasar Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin laifi a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya shaida wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗin abin da ya yi.
A cewar tuhumar, Saifov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa kallon bidiyon kungiyar IS a wayar sa ne ya sa ya kai harin.
Ya kuma nemi izinin rataye tutar kungiyar IS a dakin jinya, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a cikin tuhumar da ke kunshe da abubuwa 22.
David Patton, wani lauya na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun yi takaici da hukuncin da ofishin lauya ya yanke.
"Mun yi imanin hukuncin kisa, maimakon ɗaurin rai da rai ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba, zai ƙara saurin ciwo ga duk waɗanda ke da hannu a wannan lamarin", in ji Paton.
Kungiyar kare Saipov ta bukaci masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
