Shugaban jam'iyyar Labour, Lord Adonis, ya yi ba'a ga 'yan majalisa game da matsalolin tsaro da suka fuskanta game da shirin bikin buɗe taron.
"Waɗannan mutane ne da suka gaya mana cewa za su iya samun shirye don amfani da IT tsarin da kuma duk fasaha ga Canada da kuma da, ga wani frictionless iyaka, ga free cinikayya ba tare da iyaka a Ireland",Ya kara da cewa.
