Jirgin saman Micronesia ya yi hatsari: Air Niugini ta ce mutum daya ya bace bayan jirgin ya yi hatsari a cikin wani tafki
Kamfanin jirgin sama wanda ya yi saukar da jirgin da ya yi saukar saukar gaggawa a wani tafkin Pacific a Micronesia, ya ce duk fasinjoji 47 da ma'aikatan jirgin sun tsere lafiya daga jirgin da ke nitsewa, amma yanzu ya bayyana cewa wani fasinja ya bace ba tare da an san shi ba.
Kamfanin jirgin sama na Air Niugini ya ce a wata sanarwa da ya fitar, ya ce tun ranar Asabar ba za ta iya bayyana inda wani matashin ya ke ba.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce yana aiki tare da hukumomin yankin, asibitoci da masu bincike don gano mutumin.
Kamfanin jirgin bai bayyana cikakken bayani game da fasinja ba, kamar shekarunsa da kasa.
Jiragen ruwa na cikin gida sun taimaka wajen ceto sauran fasinjoji da ma'aikatan jirgin bayan jirgin ya yi ruwa a lokacin da yake ƙoƙarin sauka a filin jirgin saman Chuk.
A ranar Juma'a, jami'ai sun ce an kwantar da mutane bakwai a asibiti.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce fasinjoji shida sun kasance a asibiti a ranar Asabar; dukkansu suna cikin kwanciyar hankali.
Dalilin fashewar jirgin da kuma ainihin jerin abubuwan da suka faru ba a bayyana ba.
A cewar kamfanin jiragen sama da kuma rundunar sojan ruwa ta Amurka, jirgin ya sauka a cikin wani tafki ba tare da ya tashi zuwa filin saukar jiragen sama ba.
Wasu shaidu sun ce jirgin ya tsallake hanyar sauka.
Wani Ba'amurke mai tafiya a cikin jirgin, Bill Jaynes, ya ce jirgin ya yi saurin tashi.
"Wannan abu ne mai kyau", in ji Janes.
Ya ce shi da wasu sun samu damar shiga cikin ruwa har zuwa bakin jirgin da ke nitsewa.
Ya ce mataimakan jirgin sun firgita kuma suka soma ihu, kuma ya ji rauni a kansa.
Rundunar sojin ruwa ta Amurka ta ce ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa da ke gyara tashar jirgin ruwa da ke kusa da wurin sun taimaka wajen ceto ta hanyar amfani da jirgin ruwa mai dauke da iska don kwashe mutane zuwa gabar teku, har sai jirgin ya nutse a zurfin mita 30.
A cewar cibiyar tsaro ta jirgin sama, mutane 111 sun mutu a hadarin jirgin sama da aka yi rajista a Papua New Guinea a cikin shekaru ashirin da suka gabata, amma babu wani daga cikinsu da ya kasance na Air Niugini.
