Bayanan Red Tide: Rashin hankali yana raguwa a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Wani rahoto daga hukumar kula da kifi da namun daji ta Florida ya nuna raguwar yawan ruwan Red tide a wasu sassan Tampa Bay.
Kwamitin ya ba da rahoton cewa an samu wasu wurare da suka yi fure a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Callier, wanda ke nuna raguwar maida hankali.
